{"article_id":"6me2wbd7MZVqwmbv","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Architect Of Paris Attacks Was Killed In Raid ,","depth":8},{"id":1,"text":"French Authorities Say","depth":8},{"id":2,"text":"The suspected architect of the Paris attacks was killed during a violent police raid","depth":11},{"id":3,"text":"conducted by French authorities in the Paris suburb of Saint-Denis on Wednesday ,","depth":11},{"id":4,"text":"French authorities say .","depth":10},{"id":5,"text":"Abdelhamid Abaaoud was a Belgian national in his late 20s .","depth":9},{"id":6,"text":"Authorities believe","depth":9},{"id":7,"text":"that Abaaoud was close to Islamic State leader Abu Bakr al Baghdadi .","depth":9},{"id":8,"text":"During a press conference , Minister of the Interior Bernard Cazeneuve said","depth":8},{"id":9,"text":"that Abaaoud was believed to be responsible","depth":9},{"id":10,"text":"for planning many of the Islamic State attacks in Europe .","depth":9},{"id":11,"text":"Of the six planned attacks","depth":11},{"id":12,"text":"that have been foiled in France ,","depth":11},{"id":13,"text":"he said ,","depth":10},{"id":14,"text":"Abaaoud was believed to have been involved in four of them .","depth":9},{"id":15,"text":"Authorities believe","depth":9},{"id":16,"text":"he orchestrated the the three teams","depth":10},{"id":17,"text":"that attacked six locations across Paris","depth":11},{"id":18,"text":"and killed 129 people .","depth":11},{"id":19,"text":"Announcing his death ,","depth":7},{"id":20,"text":"Cazeneuve said","depth":7},{"id":21,"text":"that","depth":7},{"id":22,"text":"as promised ,","depth":8},{"id":23,"text":"`` the Republic is doing everything","depth":10},{"id":24,"text":"it can","depth":10},{"id":25,"text":"to destroy terrorism . ''","depth":9},{"id":26,"text":"The Saint-Denis raid on Wednesday were bloody and violent .","depth":6},{"id":27,"text":"Police fired more than 5,000 rounds","depth":7},{"id":28,"text":"and one suspect","depth":10},{"id":29,"text":"- presumed to be a woman -","depth":10},{"id":30,"text":"detonated a suicide vest .","depth":9},{"id":31,"text":"Another suspect ,","depth":10},{"id":32,"text":"whom we can now assume","depth":11},{"id":33,"text":"was Abaaoud ,","depth":11},{"id":34,"text":"was killed by either gunfire or a grenade explosion during the confrontation with police .","depth":9},{"id":35,"text":"Yesterday , authorities said","depth":7},{"id":36,"text":"because of the carnage ,","depth":8},{"id":37,"text":"forensic evidence had to be used","depth":9},{"id":38,"text":"to identify the dead .","depth":9},{"id":39,"text":"Today , Paris Prosecutor François Molins said","depth":7},{"id":40,"text":"that Abaaoud 's was identified","depth":8},{"id":41,"text":"using fingerprints .","depth":8},{"id":42,"text":"As we 've reported ,","depth":6},{"id":43,"text":"until recently authorities believed","depth":7},{"id":44,"text":"that Abaaoud was issuing orders from Syria .","depth":7},{"id":45,"text":"Cazeneuve said","depth":7},{"id":46,"text":"that authorities knew","depth":9},{"id":47,"text":"that he had left for Syria in 2014 ,","depth":9},{"id":48,"text":"but they had no indication","depth":9},{"id":49,"text":"that he had come back to Europe .","depth":9},{"id":50,"text":"However , three days after the Paris attacks on Nov. 16 , Cazeneuve said","depth":8},{"id":51,"text":"they received a tip from an `` intelligence service outside of Europe , ''","depth":9},{"id":52,"text":"saying","depth":10},{"id":53,"text":"they had picked up signals","depth":11},{"id":54,"text":"that Abaaoud had passed through Greece .","depth":11},{"id":55,"text":"Authorities across the world knew ,","depth":10},{"id":56,"text":"he said ,","depth":10},{"id":57,"text":"that an international warrant had been issued for Abaaoud 's arrest .","depth":9},{"id":58,"text":"The implication there is that somehow Abaaoud 's presence in Europe had fallen through the cracks .","depth":8},{"id":59,"text":"Cazeneuve added","depth":6},{"id":60,"text":"that he has called for a meeting with other European countries","depth":7},{"id":61,"text":"to talk about ways","depth":8},{"id":62,"text":"they can bolster cooperation on border controls and the fight against weapons trafficking .","depth":8},{"id":63,"text":"`` Things are not going far enough .","depth":8},{"id":64,"text":"Things are not moving fast enough , ''","depth":8},{"id":65,"text":"Cazeneuve said .","depth":7},{"id":66,"text":"`` Europe owes it to all the victims of terrorism to act . ''","depth":6},{"id":67,"text":"NPR 's Dina Temple-Raston reports","depth":5},{"id":68,"text":"that the fate of Salah Abdeslam ,","depth":7},{"id":69,"text":"whom","depth":9},{"id":70,"text":"police say","depth":9},{"id":71,"text":"was a key operative in the attacks ,","depth":8},{"id":72,"text":"is still unknown .","depth":6},{"id":73,"text":"Another unidentified suspect may also still be on the loose .","depth":4},{"id":74,"text":"Meanwhile , in Belgium , police conducted raids at six locations across Brussels , including some in the Molenbeek suburb ,","depth":5},{"id":75,"text":"which has become notorious for producing radicalized youth .","depth":5},{"id":76,"text":"NPR 's Peter Kenyon reports","depth":6},{"id":77,"text":"that officials say","depth":7},{"id":78,"text":"they are looking for associates of Bilal Hadfi , one of the Islamist attackers","depth":8},{"id":79,"text":"who died during the Paris killings on Friday .","depth":8},{"id":80,"text":"Hadfi was one of two terrorists","depth":6},{"id":81,"text":"who detonated explosive vests just outside a packed stadium in north Paris .","depth":6},{"id":82,"text":"This is a breaking news story ,","depth":4},{"id":83,"text":"we 'll update this post with the latest","depth":6},{"id":84,"text":"as we get it ,","depth":6},{"id":85,"text":"so make sure to refresh this page .","depth":5},{"id":86,"text":"Update at 8:11 a.m . ET .","depth":3},{"id":87,"text":"Lower House Votes","depth":4},{"id":88,"text":"To Extend State Of Emergency :","depth":4},{"id":89,"text":"France 's National Assembly approved President Hollande 's request","depth":6},{"id":90,"text":"to extend the state of emergency in the country by three months .","depth":6},{"id":91,"text":"The measure still has to be approved by the Senate .","depth":5},{"id":92,"text":"As NPR 's Lauren Frayer reports ,","depth":5},{"id":93,"text":"the state of emergency allows the government to :","depth":5}],"relations":[{"parent":187,"left":175,"right":186,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":175,"left":160,"right":174,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":160,"left":135,"right":159,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":135,"left":119,"right":134,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":119,"left":112,"right":118,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":112,"left":101,"right":111,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":101,"left":95,"right":100,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":95,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":100,"left":98,"right":99,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":98,"left":97,"right":5,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":97,"left":96,"right":4,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":96,"left":2,"right":3,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":99,"left":6,"right":7,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":111,"left":103,"right":110,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":103,"left":8,"right":102,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":102,"left":9,"right":10,"relation":"explanation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":110,"left":106,"right":109,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":106,"left":105,"right":14,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":105,"left":104,"right":13,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":104,"left":11,"right":12,"relation":"elaboration","